/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.processon.com/diagraming/6820d4975af9ec6a21e8b3a1&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;external nofollow noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;https://www.processon.com/diagraming/6820d4975af9ec6a21e8b3a1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
